room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: My daughter and her friends did the kidnapping over Fall break. Everyone had a great time. Now everyone, including her friends parents, want to go so we will have her birthday celebration there. It was that much fun!

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: This was my first time going and I truly had sooo much fun and will be returning soon. Gabriel was our game master for kidnapping(the room) and he was so much fun!!!

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: We just finished kidnapped, so much fun! A lot more in depth than I expected! If you are looking for a fun adventure that will force you to think then this is a game for you! Will be back for another room!!!

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: The "kidnapping" room was both challenging and a lot of fun! Will definitely be back to try the other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: My family and I went tonight and had a blast. It was a great experience. We will definitely return. Oh and we made it out of the kidnapping room with 2.5 min on the clock. Thank you!!
